beginning, containing an area of Twenty Four Thousand Two Hundred Eight (24,208) square meters, more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground by Pls cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 60 cms. Bearings Grid. Date of survey on December 1, 1987 – May 3, 1988 executed by Engr. Dominador B. Aurelio and was approved on December 16, 1991.

This proclamation shall be deemed automatically revoked or cancelled in the event that the reservation no longer serves the purpose for which it was originally established and/or has been abandoned by the said reservee and the area covered thereby be forthwith reverted to the mass of forestland under the administrative jurisdiction of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources (DENR) through its appropriate agency.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 22nd day March, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

